---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Services — Mad Learning Lab" description="Two ways we work with organizations: full-service consulting on research and evaluation, plus capacity-building to grow the skills inside your team.">
  <section class="page">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">Services</p>
    <h2 class="page-title">Two ways we work with you.</h2>

    <h3 class="service-section-title">Consulting Services</h3>
    <p>Mad Learning Lab creates custom solutions that fit your organization's evaluation needs.</p>
    <p>Our services include:</p>
    <ul class="service-list">
      <li>Analyzing data to turn raw information into useful insights</li>
      <li>Telling your impact story to share your results with stakeholders</li>
      <li>Providing independent evaluations to honestly assess how well your program works</li>
      <li>Building sustainable assessment systems</li>
      <li>Conducting research to find opportunities and guide decisions</li>
      <li>Creating plans and programs based on proven approaches</li>
      <li>Working with your team to improve their analysis skills</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Each service is designed to work with what you're already doing, helping your team make better decisions without making things too complicated.</p>
    <p>We use practical methods to get results for complex organizations like businesses, nonprofits, advocacy groups, government agencies, and public-private partnerships.</p>
    <p>Let's talk about how we can help your organization use data to show your impact and create meaningful change.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page service-section">
    <h3 class="service-section-title">Capacity Building Services</h3>
    <p>In today's nonprofit world, program managers often have to handle research, evaluation, and learning on top of their regular jobs. Our approach helps fill this gap by offering practical, customized evaluation solutions that fit easily into what you're already doing.</p>
    <p>We can help your managers with:</p>
    <ul class="service-list">
      <li>Creating Theories of Change &amp; Logic Models</li>
      <li>Developing Learning Agendas &amp; Measurement Plans</li>
      <li>Mapping Client Journeys</li>
      <li>Creating and designing data collection tools (like surveys and interviews)</li>
      <li>Analyzing data and improving data skills</li>
      <li>Systems Thinking</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our services help your team use data to make decisions without adding too much to their workload.</p>
    <p>We work with you to build skills in your team while providing useful insights that show your program's impact and help with strategic decisions.</p>
    <p>Ready to improve your evaluation practice? Let's talk about how we can support your team's specific needs.</p>
    <p class="service-cta">
      <a href="/contact" class="cta">
        Get in touch
        <span class="cta-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
